data.description: Elegant, well-appointed home in the prestigious Falcon Trace community. This home features a spacious open floor plan with views from the kitchen to the Living, Dining, Den areas and out to the backyard. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and lots of storage. The grand Master Suite is complete with (2) walk-in closets including built-ins AND a sitting area for your extra comfort. The home is equipped with built-in surround speakers extending out to the fully screened patio, ideal for entertaining. The backyard is professionally landscaped with full grown palms and clusia plants creating a privacy fence that makes for your own pristine oasis. Add a pool too if you want to take a splash. Come See This Inviting Home and Start Packing!.
